---
title: Beef and Zucchini Rigatoni with Parmesan Blush Sauce
description: This creamy, tomato-based blush sauce with ground beef and tender zucchini is a perfect, light and tasty pasta. This meal comes together quickly and is brightened up with fresh herbs!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/rigatonis-au-boeuf-et-aux-courgettes-caa544b4.jpg
